South Africans have been invested in the country’s farmers love lives since 2008. Many successful relationships were formed and beautiful families emerged, but there were also many hearts broken along the way.  As South Africa gets ready to welcome 10 new farmers on their quest to find love in Season 15 of the hugely popular television reality show Boer Soek ‘n Vrou, we take a look at some interesting facts about the show.  ALSO SEE: Cindy Nell Roberts debunks fasting myths and how she lost weight Boer Soek ’n Vrou season 15 starts on Thursday 19 January 2023 at 7pm on kykNET, channel 144 on DStv.